      <item>
        <title>Why we need hl3</title>
        <dc:creator><![CDATA[The_Scientist]]></dc:creator>
        <description><![CDATA[
            <p>I never suggested that Valve would randomly hand out their IP to any old outfit, so how about a little less arrogance Crypt?<br>
It’s not beyond the realms of possibilities for Valve and CC, or any other game studio for that matter, to work together on HL3, with Valve being the publisher. For instance, Turtle Rock studios developed Left For Dead and the game was published by Valve, which is just one example of Valve working with other devs.<br>
It’s that kind of scenario that I’m suggesting with impeccable logic as it happens.</p>
          <p><a href="https://leakfree.org/t/why-we-need-hl3/14944/17">Read full topic</a></p>
        ]]></description>
